steps.name: Given The user is on flipKart home page
When I enter productname in search bar "watch for men"
Then I must be navigated to search page
When the user sets the minimum price filter to "2000"
And sets the maximum price filter to "10000"
When the user selects the Price Low to High sorting option
Then the products displayed should have prices greater than or equal to "2000"
When the user selects the Price High to Low  sorting option
Then the products displayed should have prices less than or equal to "10000"
